                     <interp inst="t17860719-12-person202" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>Do you remember seeing the prisoner in the month of June? - I do remember seeing him very well.</p>
               <p>Be cautious? - I saw 
               <persName id="t17860719-12-person203">
                  Charles
