                  </persName>
             on the 15th of June, at Mr. 
               <persName id="t17860719-12-person204">
                  Joseph
                   Lilly
               <interp inst="t17860719-12-person204" type="surname" value="Lilly"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860719-12-person204" type="given" value="Joseph"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860719-12-person204" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            's; they invited me to dinner; I dined there; and my mother; there I saw him; I did not come from there till eleven at night; I went there about twelve at noon; he was there, and Franklin was there; I dined with him, and drank tea and supped,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178607190031"></xptr> and left him there, and he slept there that night; Mr. Lilly owed me some money; there was 
               <persName id="t17860719-12-person205">
                  Charles
                   Franklin
               <interp inst="t17860719-12-person205" type="surname" value="Franklin"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860719-12-person205" type="given" value="Charles"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860719-12-person205" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , 
               <persName id="t17860719-12-person206">
                  Lucy
                   Ward
               <interp inst="t17860719-12-person206" type="surname" value="Ward"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860719-12-person206" type="given" value="Lucy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860719-12-person206" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , 
