                     <interp inst="t17860719-12-person207" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , Mr. and Mrs. Lilly, that was all.</p>
               <p>Do you know Divine? - He did not dine there, he came in the forenoon, but did not dine.</p>
               <p>Was he there after dinner at all? - I do not know that he was there after dinner; we played at cards, several games, all fours, and cribbage; and I believe we played at whist.</p>
               <p>Who was your party at whist? - Mrs. Lilly was my partner; we played in turns.</p>
